<p>
Komatsu Architecture has successfully executed design-build programs since 1988. We have been able to establish successful working relationships to complete all programs.
</br></br>
Our design teams have completed over $250 million in design/build construction on DOD facilities, and another $200 million on private sector design-build and construction manager programs where Komatsu has participated in the contractor selection process.
</br></br>
All programs have been executed within the contract schedules.  Our range of teaming design-build partners is geographically diverse, from the CONUS Northern Tier to all five Conus geographic regions, and for OCONUS programs in the Pacific Rim.
</br></br>
With these projects, we have maintained the same project delivery leadership personnel, bringing proven, effective, knowledgeable resources that we propose to bring to your Design-Build program.
</p>
